OL,3,CHealth visitors left with 'no choice'
OL,4,Cbut strike action amid pay banding row
OL,6,FHealth visitors say they have been
OL,7,Fleft with "no choice" but to take four
OL,8,Fweeks of strike action amid a pay
OL,9,Fbanding row.
OL,11,FWorkers employed by Cwm Taf Morgannwg
OL,12,FUniversity Health Board began
OL,13,Findustrial action on February 23 over
OL,14,Fan incorrect pay banding "costing them
OL,15,Fthousands", according to Unite union.
OL,17,FThe union says health visitors are
OL,18,Fmissing out on between #8,000 and
OL,19,F#9,000 a year their NHS employer is
OL,20,Frefusing to pay them the correct
OL,21,Fsalary based on their qualifications.
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@UO]vD@ZOUwD@JO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/12
