FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1771879288
OL,3,CHealth visitors left with 'no choice'
OL,4,Cbut strike action amid pay banding row
OL,6,FOne health worker taking industrial
OL,7,Faction said: "Everybody who knows me,
OL,8,Fknows how much I love my job, so this
OL,9,Fhas been such a big decision. It's not
OL,10,Fsomething that we've taken lightly -
OL,11,Fit isn't about the money, it's about
OL,12,Fwhat we deserve and it's about valuing
OL,13,Fthe profession and protecting the
OL,14,Fprofession for the future as well."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
