CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1771879288
OL,3,CHealth visitors left with 'no choice'
OL,4,Cbut strike action amid pay banding row
OL,6,FHer colleague, also striking, added:
OL,7,F"We're advocates for these children in
OL,8,Four communities and we know that we
OL,9,Fcould have a huge impact by not being
OL,10,Fin work - we worry about that and
OL,11,Fwe're worrying about it right now. We
OL,12,Fwant to get back out there so please
OL,13,FCTM, listen."
OL,15,FWith strike action potentially lasting
OL,16,Ffor the next four weeks, mothers in
OL,17,Fthe Cwm Taf Morgannwg health board
OL,18,Farea told ITV Wales of their fears of
OL,19,Fbeing left without health visitors.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
