SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1771879288
OL,3,CHealth visitors left with 'no choice'
OL,4,Cbut strike action amid pay banding row
OL,6,FEmma Moore, class leader at Story
OL,7,FBabies Bridgend, said health visitors
OL,8,Fwere a "lifeline" for her when her
OL,9,Fbaby was unwell.
OL,11,F"It's a very scary time for some of
OL,12,Four mums at the moment," she said.
OL,13,F"The health visitors are a lifeline
OL,14,Ffor them, an absolute resource.
OL,16,F"I think that there's definitely a lot
OL,17,Fof worried mums out there, that
OL,18,Fwithout that network to fall back on,
OL,19,Fwithout that support, what might they
OL,20,Fdo in an emergency?"
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@QO]sD@AOUtD@XO]uD@AOUxD@AOU|D@
