OL,3,CHealth visitors left with 'no choice'
OL,4,Cbut strike action amid pay banding row
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV Wales, sent direct
OL,9,Fto your inbox every Saturday morning.
OL,11,FMum of a five-month-old, Rhiannon
OL,12,FWalker, says her regular baby groups
OL,13,Fhave been cancelled due to the strikes
OL,14,Fand feels "vulnerable".
OL,16,FShe added: "If I need support, getting
OL,17,Fa GP appointment is not easy, so it's
OL,18,Fmade us quite worried. If I have any
OL,19,Fconcerns, where do I go?"
OL,26,@vD@KOUvD@VO]xD@LOU{D@YO]
