OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1771879288
OL,3,CHealth visitors left with 'no choice'
OL,4,Cbut strike action amid pay banding row
OL,6,FUnite says the current dispute is also
OL,7,Fheavily linked to the previous dispute
OL,8,Fwith the CTM Health Board where staff
OL,9,Fhad to take historic industrial action
OL,10,Fover unsustainable workloads.
OL,12,FPaul Seppman, Unite regional officer,
OL,13,Fsaid: "This is not a position our
OL,14,Fmembers want to be in but are now left
OL,15,Fwith no choice when they are being
OL,16,Funderpaid thousands of pounds a year.
OL,17,FCwm Taf Morgannwg has acted shamefully
OL,18,Ftowards a group of female staff, who
OL,19,Fhave now stood up against this
OL,20,Fappalling behaviour.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1771879288
OL,3,CHealth visitors left with 'no choice'
OL,4,Cbut strike action amid pay banding row
OL,6,F"This campaign will not stop at CTMUHB
OL,7,Fwith this quickly becoming a national
OL,8,Fissue. Unite are taking this issue
OL,9,Facross all health boards in Wales and
OL,10,Furging staff to join Unite the union
OL,11,Fand become part of the campaign to be
OL,12,Fpaid what members rightfully deserve."
OL,14,FA spokesperson for Cwm Taf Morgannwg
OL,15,FUniversity Health Board said: "The
OL,16,Fhealth board has been in discussion
OL,17,Fwith Unite and health visiting staff
OL,18,Fsince a formal dispute was lodged in
OL,19,FFebruary 2024.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1771879288
OL,3,CHealth visitors left with 'no choice'
OL,4,Cbut strike action amid pay banding row
OL,6,F"The dispute asked for the Band 6
OL,7,Fhealth visitor job description to be
OL,8,Fupdated to reflect the duties of the
OL,9,Frole, and to re-evaluate the job. A
OL,10,Fprocess to review and agree the
OL,11,Frevised job description took place,
OL,12,Ffacilitated by NHS Wales Employers.
OL,14,F"The job description, which was agreed
OL,15,Fin social partnership, was re-
OL,16,Fevaluated, and came out at the same
OL,17,Fband, Band 6. The job description was
OL,18,Fissued to health visiting staff and
OL,19,Fremains in effect.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1771879288
OL,3,CHealth visitors left with 'no choice'
OL,4,Cbut strike action amid pay banding row
OL,6,F"The health board is aware that over
OL,7,Frecent years, there have been changes
OL,8,Fmade to education requirements for
OL,9,Fhealth visitors as a result of
OL,10,Fdecisions taken by the Nursing and
OL,11,FMidwifery Council, which have more
OL,12,Frecently impacted national profiles
OL,13,Ffor health visitor roles.
OL,15,F"The health board is committed to
OL,16,Fworking through the implications of
OL,17,Fthese changes in social partnership,
OL,18,Fas part of national discussions with
OL,19,Ftrade unions.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1771879288
OL,3,CHealth visitors left with 'no choice'
OL,4,Cbut strike action amid pay banding row
OL,6,F"We respect the rights of colleagues
OL,7,Fto take industrial action and will
OL,8,Fwork with teams to minimise disruption
OL,9,Fto families across our communities as
OL,10,Frequired."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/12
